import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import Card from "./Cards";
import './index.css';

ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <Card
      imgsrc="https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp4056410.jpg"
      sname="DARK"
      title="A Netflix Original Series"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172"
    />

    <Card
      imgsrc="https://resizing.flixster.com/xuVpm0Fy4aul1tzPlhVyorexEmk=/206x305/v2/https://resizing.flixster.com/9_UFhNH0nIQR71Jn-w94AJZbDFI=/ems.cHJkLWVtcy1hc3NldHMvdHZzZWFzb24vUlRUVjcwMjA0Ny53ZWJw"
      sname="EXTRA CURRICULAR"
      title="A Netflix Original Series"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80990668?source=35"
    />

    <Card
      imgsrc="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/movie-poster-design_841014-8874.jpg?w=360"
      sname="STRANGER THINGS"
      title="A Netflix Original Series"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057281"
    />
  </>,
  document.getElementById("root")
);
